            <text display-inline="yes-display-inline">The table of sections for <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/ch:1/sch:A/pt:IV/spt:C">subpart C of part
