        <text><cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:6038/ss:a/p:1/sp:B">Subparagraph (B) of section 6038(a)(1)</cato:entity-ref> is amended by
